Ok then, let’s get right into it and tell the story of Geli Raubal.

00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:58.003
On September 19th, 1931, the police pushed open the door of an apartment in Munich, in Germany.

00:00:59.173 --> 00:01:01.883
There was an eerie silence in the air.

00:01:02.533 --> 00:01:03.523
